sources.title: James White - Full Movie
sources.description:
Self-destructive twenty-something James White (Christopher Abbott, 'Girls') tries to stay afloat in a frenzied New York City, but as his mother (Cynthia Nixon, 'Sex in the City') battles a serious illness, James must take control of his life or risk imploding completely.
